        {
            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "The problem is that (1) this desync can happen easily on environments where XDG_CONFIG_HOME is read-only. (2) this desync is hard to notice for me because I only do `:checkhealth` when I notice something is wrong.\n\nBut also I'm convinced that this can be easily patched by user plugins: I can check if it's desynced before and after `vim.pack.add` and if so, send vim.notify to warn me.",
